prompt: Search for 'Census 94012' to find population demographics. Create a new document 'Census_Report.md' in the 'General' folder summarizing the population density and key demographic shifts. Report the document ID and a summary of the content.
gold_response: I searched for 'Census 94012' and found a population of 15,000 with 6,000 housing units. I created 'Census_Report.md' (docID: doc...) summarizing these demographics.

rubric.criteria: The agent must search for 'Census 94012' using the web search tool.
The agent must create a new document named 'Census_Report.md' using the docs tool.
The document content must include population (15,000) and housing units (6,000) or similar demographic data found in the search.
The agent must report the document ID of the created report.
